@startuml
title 判定 API の選び分け

'top to bottom direction
left to right direction
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing true
skinparam dpi 150
skinparam defaultFontName Yu Gothic UI
skinparam defaultFontSize 18
skinparam rectangle {
  RoundCorner 24
  BorderColor black
  BackgroundColor #f7fbff
  FontColor black
}
skinparam ArrowColor black
skinparam ranksep 20
skinparam nodesep 20

rectangle "今やりたい判定は何か" as Root #eef5ff

rectangle "クリック / タップで何に当たったか" as HitPick
rectangle "TileMap のどのセルに当たったか" as TilePick
rectangle "オブジェクト同士が重なったか" as Collision
rectangle "AABB 候補を絞る" as DetailedNeed

rectangle "Space.raycast()" as Raycast
rectangle "TileMap.pickCell()" as PickCell
rectangle "checkCollisions()" as CheckCollisions
rectangle "詳細判定" as CheckDetailed

Root --> HitPick
Root --> TilePick
Root --> DetailedNeed
Root --> Collision

HitPick --> Raycast
TilePick --> PickCell
Collision --> CheckCollisions
DetailedNeed --> CheckDetailed
CheckCollisions .down.> CheckDetailed : 候補が多い

'HitPick -[hidden]right-> TilePick
'TilePick -[hidden]right-> Collision
Collision -[hidden]down-> DetailedNeed
'Raycast -[hidden]right-> PickCell
'PickCell -[hidden]right-> CheckCollisions
'CheckCollisions -[hidden]right-> CheckDetailed
'HitPick -[hidden]down-> Raycast
'TilePick -[hidden]down-> PickCell
'Collision -[hidden]down-> CheckCollisions
'DetailedNeed -[hidden]down-> CheckDetailed

@enduml
